n next 5 stitches, single crochet 2 together] repeat 6 times. (36 stitches)","Ball — Round 17: [Single crochet in next 4 stitches, single crochet 2 together] repeat 6 times. (30 stitches)","Ball — Round 18: [Single crochet in next 3 stitches, single crochet 2 together] repeat 6 times. (24 stitches)","Ball — Round 19: [Single crochet in next 2 stitches, single crochet 2 together] repeat 6 times. (18 stitches)","Ball — Stuffing: Stuff firmly with polyfill, shaping as you go. Keep adding stuffing as the opening closes.","Ball — Round 20: [Single crochet in next stitch, single crochet 2 together] repeat 6 times. (12 stitches)","Ball — Round 21: [Single crochet 2 together] repeat 6 times. (6 stitches)","Ball — Finishing: Fasten off leaving a long tail. Thread the tail through the front loops of the remaining 6 stitches, pull tight to close, and weave in the end."]', '2026-06-30T00:00:00.000Z')
