6 stitches each round) Join with a slip stitch at the end of each round.","Beanie — Change to cream yarn.","Beanie — Rounds 47–48: Chain 2 (does not count as a stitch), single crochet in each stitch around. (96 stitches each round) Join with a slip stitch at the end of each round.","Beanie — Brim: Work 2 rounds of single crochet in each stitch around for a clean edge. (96 stitches each round) Fasten off and weave in ends."]', '2026-06-30T00:00:00.000Z')
